{"tid":526964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（升級騙局？）iPhone推iOS 11更新　外國用戶指降速達五成","createTime":"2018-01-12T07:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T14:03:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"26d46c83b863b38fd60c8dbd07be742bdd371e92","tid":526964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"01月11日(四) 19:51   <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/151947_28c1f64515f52581cf72549606d52f55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F151947_28c1f64515f52581cf72549606d52f55.png&h=6ca6522a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國晶片製造商英特爾(Intel)日前承認，公司近年生產的晶片存有保安漏洞。蘋果公司亦指晶片漏洞對旗下的電腦Mac及iOS系統有影響，推出iOS 11.2.2正式版更新，主要修復Safari瀏覽器的「Spectre」安全漏洞。有外國媒體報道指，有不少外國網民在Twitter引用跑分數據反映，其iPhone在升級到iOS 11.2.2之後，效能出現下滑迹象，部分人更聲稱iPhone的性能甚至下降50%。 <br />\n<br />\n然而亦有少部分網友表示，其iPhone的跑分在升級之後反而上升。針對此情況，該媒體認為如果iPhone原本就是iOS 11的系統，建議還是升級到iOS 11.2.2；但如果目前仍處於iOS 10的話，則暫時不要升級。"},{"pid":"c20030e6335ed906f4b038b7a96e365d85227f65","tid":526964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c392a0183a73a0290190bb23edd84536cdb086b","tid":526964,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"26d46c83b863b38fd60c8dbd07be742bdd371e92","tid":526964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"01月11日(四) 19:51   <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/151947_28c1f64515f52581cf72549606d52f55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F151947_28c1f64515f52581cf72549606d52f55.png&h=6ca6522a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國晶片製造商英特爾(Intel)日前承認，公司近年生產的晶片存有保安漏洞。蘋果公司亦指晶片漏洞對旗下的電腦Mac及iOS系統有影響，推出iOS 11.2.2正式版更新，主要修復Safari瀏覽器的「Spectre」安全漏洞。有外國媒體報道指，有不少外國網民在Twitter引用跑分數據反映，其iPhone在升級到iOS 11.2.2之後，效能出現下滑迹象，部分人更聲稱iPhone的性能甚至下降50%。 <br />\n<br />\n然而亦有少部分網友表示，其iPhone的跑分在升級之後反而上升。針對此情況，該媒體認為如果iPhone原本就是iOS 11的系統，建議還是升級到iOS 11.2.2；但如果目前仍處於iOS 10的話，則暫時不要升級。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"升11.2.2完個分高左40<br />\n<br />\niPhone SE"},{"pid":"1f34a0b38cc1461c3b278904cc42d81d4ef0a2d2","tid":526964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dac869911994d7179626b06f9a8e9725f8a405","tid":526964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8742a46ea582c06772f26b5abe40a63dcef089","tid":526964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f6dc9fbc6c3ef8259eb86c599b906a66841382","tid":526964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}